Starbucks nutrition

Source: R/data-starbucks.R
starbucks.Rd

Nutrition facts for several Starbucks food items

starbucks

Format

A data frame with 77 observations on the following 7 variables.

item

Food item.

calories

Calories.

fat

a numeric vector

carb

a numeric vector

fiber

a numeric vector

protein

a numeric vector

type

a factor with levels bakery, bistro box, hot breakfast, parfait, petite, salad, and sandwich

Source

https://www.starbucks.com/menu, retrieved 2011-03-10.

Examples


starbucks
